ttp://www.clanorderofice.com/wow">http://www.clanorderofice.com/wow</a> check out our website if you wish to join click on the Join Clan Ice link and follow the instructions. If you wish to learn more about us register at our message boards and ask away. We are also interested in alliances with guilds that have similar interests. <br> <p>&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr align="right" valign="bottom"><td colspan=2 class="BoardRowB"><a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/post.asp?brd=22641&topic=77309583">Post Reply</a> | <a href="/active_topic_notify.asp?mes=77309583" class="BoardRowBLink">Active Topic Notification</a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/pm_send.asp?usr=972556">Private Message</a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/user_posts.asp?usr=972556">Post History</a></td></tr><tr align="left" valign="top" class="BoardRowA"><td class="BoardRowA" rowspan=3 width="17%"><a href=" http://users.ign.com/about/Gorgrim_Warcry?boards=vn " class="AuthorLink">Gorgrim_Warcry</a>&nbsp;<br><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><!-- WISH & COLL STUFF --><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tr class="BoardRowA"><td nowrap="false" class="BoardRowA"><a class="BoardRowBLink" href="http://users.ign.com/collection/Gorgrim_Warcry"><font size="1">collection (0)</font></a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="http://users.ign.com/wishlist/Gorgrim_Warcry"><font size="1">wishlist (0)</font></a></td></tr></table><!-- /WISH & COLL STUFF	--><span style="font-weight: bold;">Posts:</span> 7<br><span style="font-weight: bold;">Registered:</span> Oct 04<br></span><br></td><td class="BoardRowA" colspan=2 width="83%"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Date Posted:</span>&nbsp;10/21 2:46am&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: bold;">Subject:</span> RE: Clan Ice now recruiting </td></tr><tr valign=top><td class="BoardRowB" colspan=2 width="83%">More site updates, check us out !! <br> <p>&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr align="right" valign="bottom"><td colspan=2 class="BoardRowB"><a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/post.asp?brd=226